name: Lolita necklace-Wp
description:
This simple & subtle layered necklace is made up of 14K goldfill and strategically placed lustrous, white freshwater pearls. Drop "down" gorgeous!

Length of this necklace is 16" with an extention to 17.5"

name: A1 necklace-Wp
description:
A white, teardrop-shaped freshwater pearl dangles from a fine, goldfilled chain.
This necklace is 18 inches in length.
If you'd like the chain in a different length, please contact me. I'd be happy to customize it.

name: Alex necklace-Wp
description:
A classic white pearl necklace with a playful touch. Wrapped between and dangling from a 14k goldfill chain these delicious freshwater pearls have beautiful luster. 

Length is 16 inches with an extention at 17.5 inches.

name: A1 necklace-Sp
description:
A silver colored, coin-shaped freshwater pearl is the focus point in this goldfilled, 18-inch necklace.
Please contact me for a price quote regarding a different length of chain

name: A1 necklace-Gp
description:
This goldfilled necklace is 18 inches in length. It features a beautiful peacock-blue teardrop pendant.
If you'd like the necklace in a different size, please le me know, so I can give you a price quote.

name: Siena necklace-LGmSp
description: This 14K goldfill necklace is made up of beautiful, faceted gray moonstones, glowing labradorites and shiny, smooth freshwater pearls. The length (about 58 inches) and toggle clasp make it possible to wear this necklace in many different ways; as a lariat, or wrapped around once.. twice...three times.

name: B16 necklace-L
description:
An iridescent labradorite briolette, wrapped in 14K goldfilled wire, dangles from a fine, 18 inch, goldfilled chain. 
Size of the stone is about 3/4th of an inch in length and half an inch at its widest point.
If you'd like the chain to be a different length, please let me know, so I can give you a price quote.

name: Stone/pearl necklace-SpL
description: This long necklace features an iridescent, faceted labradorite briolette attached to a lustrous, coin-shaped freshwater pearl. The large loop of the pendant is strengthened with 14K goldfilled wire-wrapping. Total length of the fine, goldfilled chain is 24 inches.

name: Ginger necklace-SqWpBp
description:
A beautifully wrapped small smokey quartz briolette dangles from the middle of this tiered necklace, complemented by white and bronze freshwater pearls.

The length of this necklace is 16 inches, with an extention to 17.5 inches.

name: C16 necklace-O
description:
An onyx briolette, wrapped generously in 14K goldfilled wire, is the focus in this necklace. 
The stone is about an inch from top to bottom, and almost 3/4th of an inch at its widest point.
It hangs from a fine chain with a total length of 18 inches.
Please let me know if you'd prefer a different length. I'd be happy to customize the necklace for you.

name: Lilyan necklace-O
description:
The pendant on this goldfilled necklace features two faceted, black onyx stones and a hammered goldfilled ring. Both stones are wrapped in 14K goldfilled wire. Length of the chain is 18 inches.
If you prefer another length, please let me know. I'll be happy to make it just right for you.

name: Lilyan necklace-Cq
description:
This necklace features a beautiful, faceted crystal quartz teardrop, hanging from a hammered ring surrounding another generously wrapped, crystal quartz stone.
This goldfilled necklace has a total length of 18 inches.

name: Julia necklace-RqSp
description: This subtle and stunning 14K goldfill lariat features faceted rose quartz beads and generously wrapped briolettes, complemented by gorgeous silver toned freshwater pearls.

name: C16 necklace-Rq
description:
A faceted, wire-wrapped rose quartz briolette dangles from a fine, goldfilled chain.
The stone meaures about an inch from top to bottom, and almost 3/4th of an inch at its widest point. The length of this necklace is 18 inches.
Please contact me if you would like this necklace in a different length.

name: Lily necklace-Rq
description: A translucent, faceted rosequartz briolette inside a hammered goldfilled ring is the focus point in this necklace. Total length of the fine, goldfilled chain is 18 inches.

name: Lily necklace-Az
description: This necklace features a wire-wrapped, opaque amazonite stone inside a hammered goldfilled ring. The pendant hangs from an 18 inch, fine, goldfilled chain. Different lengths are available.

name: Hilary necklace-CaAzGa
description:
Summer is here! The tropical color combo in this necklace makes it a great piece for a beautiful, sunny summer day.
This necklace hosts translucent carnelian beads, together with faceted amazonites and clear green amethysts. A generously wrapped amazonite is the centerpiece of a 14k goldfill, hammered oval. 

This necklace is 16.5 inches in length, with an extention to 18 inches.

name: C16 necklace-Ra
description:
This necklace features a beautifully wrapped, red agate briolette pendant.
The stone is about an inch in length,and almost 3/4th of an inch at its widest point. 
It hangs from a fine, 18 inch long, goldfilled chain.
Please contact me if you'd prefer this necklace in a different size.

name: Gili necklace-ACpSp
description:
This necklace features beautiful clear amethyst briolettes, wrapped in 14K goldfill, complemented by smooth, champagne and silver toned freshwater pearls.

Length of this necklace is 16.5 inches, with an extention to 18 inches.

name: Siena necklace-ACpGpSp
description:
Deep purple, faceted amethysts and beautiful lustrous freshwater pearls are featured in this stunning 14K goldfilled necklace.

Total length is about 58 inches, which makes it a necklace with many different looks. Wrap it around up to three times, or simply open the toggle clasp and knot it over like a lariat.

name: Reyna necklace-ACaOqCp

A waterfall of radiant color tones. 
Bright orange carnelian beads and red agate briolettes are complemented by deep purple, shimmering amethysts, translucent olive quartz' and lustrous freshwater pearls. 
A true statement necklace.

Lenght is 16.5 inches, with an extention to 18 inches.

name: C4 oval earrings-CaAz
description:
An opaque amazonite briolette, wrapped in 14K goldfill is the centerpiece of a hammered oval shape. They are attached to a faceted, radiant carnelian roundel, dangling from a 14k goldfill lever-back.

These earrings measure a little over 2 inches from top of lever-back to bottom of 14k goldfill oval shape.

name: H1 earrings-TqLGmSp
description:
These stunning eye-catchers are made up of shiny, smooth freshwater pearls, glowing gray moonstones, labradorites and tourmalinated quartz, wrapped beautifully in 14K goldfill wire.

Total length of the earrings including lever-backs is 3.25-3.5 inches.
